{"tid":1164480,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"致逝去寵物的信 （巴絲留言箱）","createTime":"2019-05-21T06:23:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-21T06:23:14.000Z","uid":50076,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"21fe5d70c928956c514be45fa58ae2f846b0f058","tid":1164480,"uid":50076,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T06:23:14.000Z","msg":"人寵相遇，乃是緣份。<br />\n<br />\n兩位貓仔，你主人我好掛住你呀，唔知你係天堂玩得開唔開心？ 好想再一次抱住你地，聞下你地浸臭貓味，同埋抱起你地唔比你落地整古你地。<br />\n<br />\n你地都知自己叫咩名，一叫你地就會望住我貓幾聲，等我有一日走左既時候，我再黎搵你地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n好傷心呀，你主人我唔想再咁sad<br />\n<br />\n歡迎巴絲留低你想同前主子講既野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}